#
# meaning of tag meta in html
#
1) <meta> is used in html <head> to accelerate running of the SearchEngine etc.

2) <meta> mainly has 'name' and 'http-equiv' two categories.
    for <meta name="..." content="...">:
        name could be keywords, description, robots, author etc.
        
    for <meta http-equiv="..." content="...">:
        http-equiv could be content-type, content-language, refresh, expires, 
                            pragma, set-cookie, window-target, cache-control etc.

